OL,6,FTemperatures in Wales dropped to -6.5
OL,7,Fovernight on Thursday, 9 January, on
OL,8,Fwhat was the UK's coldest January
OL,9,Fnight in 15 years.
OL,11,FThe Met Office had issued several snow
OL,12,Fand ice weather warnings for the
OL,13,Fcountry across the week, with
OL,14,Fforecasters warning the cold snap is
OL,15,Fset to continue.
