OL,6,FWales actually experienced its coldest
OL,7,Fnight of the winter on Wednesday, 8
OL,8,FJanuary, with temperatures dropping to
OL,9,F-7.9C in Sennybridge, Powys. This
OL,10,Frose slightly overnight on Thursday
OL,11,Fwhere lows of -6.5C were recorded in
OL,12,FHawarden Airport, Clwyd, and
OL,13,FSennybridge.
