OL,3,CTemperatures in Wales drop to -7.9C
OL,4,Cas schools closed in cold snap
OL,6,FAs well as school closures, there has
OL,7,Fbeen disruption to roads with the A44
OL,8,Fbetween Ponterwyd and Nant-yr-Arian in
OL,9,FCeredigion closed until further notice
OL,10,Fafter a HGV left the carriageway.
OL,12,FCar insurer RAC also said it had seen
OL,13,Fthe highest levels of demand for
OL,14,Frescues in a three-day period since
OL,15,FDecember 2022.
OL,17,FOn Thursday, Transport for Wales
OL,18,Fclosed some railway lines in the
OL,19,Fcountry due to track damage following
OL,20,Fa period of "heavy wind, rain and
OL,21,Fsnow".
