OL,3,CTemperatures in Wales drop to -7.9C
OL,4,Cas schools closed in cold snap
OL,6,FThe Met Office has said Friday will
OL,7,Fsee "the start of a change to our
OL,8,Fweather" with milder temperatures
OL,9,F"attempting to move in from the south
OL,10,Fwest through the morning". But this is
OL,11,Fexpected to only make "limited
OL,12,Fprogress" and patchy rain, sleet and
OL,13,Fsnow is expected across parts of the
OL,14,FUK over the weekend and into next week.
